kw.msg:
Issue URL Impact Tags
aria-allowed-role - Ensures role attribute has an appropriate value for the element Link minor cat.aria best-practice
Element Affected
1) Target: .qr-button role button is not allowed for given element

Issue URL Impact Tags
autocomplete-valid - Ensure the autocomplete attribute is correct and suitable for the form field Link serious cat.forms wcag21aa wcag135
Element Affected
1) Target: #user_password the autocomplete value is inappropriate for this type of input

Issue URL Impact Tags
bypass - Ensures each page has at least one mechanism for a user to bypass navigation and jump straight to the content Link serious cat.keyboard wcag2a wcag241 section508 section508.22.o
Element Affected
1) Target: html No valid skip link found Page does not have a header Page does not have a landmark region

Issue URL Impact Tags
color-contrast - Ensures the contrast between foreground and background colors meets WCAG 2 AA contrast ratio thresholds Link serious cat.color wcag2aa wcag143
Element Affected
1) Target: .new_session__divider-text Element has insufficient color contrast of 1.83 (foreground color: #bfbfbf, background color: #ffffff, font size: 12.0pt, font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 4.5:1

Issue URL Impact Tags
html-has-lang - Ensures every HTML document has a lang attribute Link serious cat.language wcag2a wcag311
Element Affected
1) Target: html The element does not have a lang attribute

Issue URL Impact Tags
landmark-one-main - Ensures the page has only one main landmark and each iframe in the page has at most one main landmark Link moderate cat.semantics best-practice
Element Affected
1) Target: html Page does not have a main landmark

Issue URL Impact Tags
page-has-heading-one - Ensure that the page, or at least one of its frames contains a level-one heading Link moderate cat.semantics best-practice
Element Affected
1) Target: html Page must have a level-one heading

Issue URL Impact Tags
region - Ensures all page content is contained by landmarks Link moderate cat.keyboard best-practice
Element Affected
1) Target: html Some page content is not contained by landmarks
kw.doc: Inserts readable accessibility result into `log.html` based on given `type`. Need to be used after `Run Accessibility Tests` keyword
